UOTE END--><br><br>The Initiate Symbol is yours. Free. <br><br>I completed the quest for the Initiate Symbol of Bertoxxulous. <br><br>I'm a Gnome Necromancer of Bertox.... I'm NOT even a cleric, I'm possibly the first person on the entire server to have completed this extremely frustrating &quot;newbie quest&quot;. But I did it for the challenge, and because it helped me raise factions with both Dark Reflection as well as TheDead. <br><br>Im holding the Symbol in the Bank, for any future cleric of Bertoxxulous who might need it. I personally have no use for it, since I cannot use it myself. <br><br>Also, the Symbol is no longer NODROP (server rules). Which means I can give you the one I have, and I can keep doing this quest to get another Symbol. <br><br>If you instead want me to help you DO the quest... I can do that also. It's just a matter of gathering components in Steamfont. I have no idea if a human cleric of Bertox would be KOS by the Gnomish guards. I doubt it, unless you were a really hated class like a necro or SK. <br><br>Gnome guards faction is easy to raise... kill goblins, kill aqua goblins, kill riptide goblins, and kill any Steamfont minotaurs. Easy to raise if its necessary. <br><br>If you are not KOS to the Gnome guards to start with, then chances are good that your starting faction with Evil Gnomes are even better.... you probably can train and hang out in the Mines of Malfunction. <br><br>But..... Maladominus has suffered a recent tragedy...tho I will be back shortly once a GM resolves my problem...<br><br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/urhaxalygen.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Rhaxalygen</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 133<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(1/25/02 10:36:08 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1192.to